import React from 'react'
import { Navbar,NavDropdown,Container,Nav } from 'react-bootstrap';
import './Navarapp.css'
const Navbarapp = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" bg="dark" variant="dark">
  <Container>
  <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Inicio</Navbar.Brand>
  <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
  <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
    <Nav className="me-auto">
      <Nav.Link href="#features">Aprendices</Nav.Link>
      <Nav.Link href="#pricing">Competencias</Nav.Link>
      <NavDropdown title="Desarrollo del Aprendiz" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">
        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Calificaciones</NavDropdown.Item>
        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Cualidades</NavDropdown.Item>
        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Reportes</NavDropdown.Item>
        <NavDropdown.Divider />
        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">Guia del Aprendiz</NavDropdown.Item>
      </NavDropdown>
    </Nav>
    <Nav>
      <Nav.Link href="#deets"></Nav.Link>
      <Nav.Link eventKey={2} href="#memes">
        Cuadro de Honor
      </Nav.Link>
    </Nav>
  </Navbar.Collapse>
  </Container>
</Navbar>
        </>
    )

}

export default Navbarapp
